      "role": "user",
      "content": "i keep having this weird dream every single night lately. it’s like i’m in a supermarket and i can’t stop seeing the same logo for that one energy drink brand. like the bright neon green one. it’s so vivid it actually feels real and i woke up feeling like i was actually there. has anyone else ever experienced stuff like this? it’s starting to freak me out",
