      "role": "user",
      "content": "That \"psychological imprinting\" idea is terrifying. If they can do that with just a logo, what else can they do? I feel like I can't even trust my own thoughts anymore if they're being planted while I'm unconscious. How would they even broadcast something like that so specifically to just one person? It feels so personal, like they're targeting me specifically.",
